About authors;Про авторів;О авторах;
BlockChain Wallet was created by a group of four students who are currently studying at the National University Zaporizhzhya Polytechnic". The ideological inspirer was Nikita Khalizev, the work on the software functionality was done by Daniil Potapov, the interaction between the files and the program was organized by Evgeny Latyshev, and the visual component was responsible for Azmanov Ilya. The goal of BlockChain Wallet is to popularize the use of electronic wallets among NUZP students.
